Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 4
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: This series, based on a video game, presents the legal adventures of Mr. Wright and his beautiful assistant Maya Fey.
Title: PHOENIX WRIGHT, ACE ATTORNEY, VOL. 4
Author: Kenji Kuroda

Description: A gaggle of female ninjas plot to bring Raizo, the illegitimate son of a ruling family, to power.
Title: NINJA GIRLS, VOL. 9
Author: Hosana Tanaka

Description: Naruto is in the middle of a great war — and the opposing side has a horde of animated dead ninjas.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 55
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A social agency in Italy is taking in young girl and turning them into assassins. Meet their latest: Henrietta, who comes equipped with cybernetic technology.
Title: GUNSLINGER GIRL, OMNIBUS VOL. 4
Author: Yu Aida

Description: Akitsu Masanosuke is a samurai without a lord. Will he run into more trouble when he becomes the bodyguard of the leader of the mysterious "Five Leaves" gang?
Title: HOUSE OF FIVE LEAVES, VOL. 6
Author: Natsume Ono

Description: Introducing Christie Holmes, the niece of Sherlock Holmes, who sometimes aides her uncle in solving his mysteries when not working on her own.
Title: YOUNG MISS HOLMES, CASEBOOK 1-2
Author: Kaoru Shintani

Description: Luna is a secret agent grown in a lab and has 15 years of training. Her new mission: high school!
Title: AMAZING AGENT LUNA, OMNIBUS VOL. 3
Author: Nunzio DeFilippis

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.” In this volume, the crew decide to train harder. The reward? New enemies and adventures.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 61
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 13
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji
